headline: Keysight and MediaTek Advance AI‑Driven Uplink Optimization and Model Life Cycle Management for Radio Access Networks
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., February 27, 2026--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) and MediaTek announced a working prototype that advances AI‑driven uplink optimization and model life cycle management for next‑generation radio access networks (RAN). headline: QBTS Q4 Earnings Miss Estimates, Revenue Rise Y/Y, Stock Climbs
summary: D-Wave Quantum posts a wider-than-expected Q4 loss as revenues rise 19% but miss estimates. The stock climbs 2.5% as cash surges and January bookings top $30M.
